Package: Rcodex
Type: Package
Title: Translate natural language to Rcode with Codex(OpenAI)
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Hugo Amorim
Maintainer: The package maintainer <hugo@protonmail.com>
Description: Codex is a tool that allows users to write code in a natural language,
   such as English, and have it automatically translated into a programming language,
   such as Python or R. 
   The goal of RCodex is to make it easier for people who are not familiar with a
   particular programming language to write code by allowing them to use a more
   familiar, natural language instead. 
   Codex uses natural language processing (NLP) techniques to understand the user's
